GSMA RCS Terminal API

Packages
org.gsma.joyn The RCS service is implemented into an Android background service which offers a high level API: the RCS Terminal API.
org.gsma.joyn.capability This API permits to discover capabilities supported by remote contacts.
org.gsma.joyn.chat This API exposes all functionality for single chat and group chat services.
org.gsma.joyn.contacts This API exposes all infos related to joyn contacts.
org.gsma.joyn.ft This API exposes all functionality to transfer files in real time.
org.gsma.joyn.ish This API exposes exposes all functionality related to transferring images during a CS call via the Image Share service.
org.gsma.joyn.session This API exposes all functionality to initiate multimedia sessions between two end points based on a dedicated service ID (or feature tag).
org.gsma.joyn.vsh This API exposes all functionality related to sharing live video stream during a CS call via the Video Share service.
